<div class="callout"><p><strong>Decision threshold:</strong> If the highest-scoring vendor isn't 15%+ ahead of the runner-up, run a 30-day pilot with the top two. The cost of pilot is far lower than the cost of picking wrong.</p></div>
</div></section>

